      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm looking into some Portland municipal codes. Can you explain how mixed-use zoning works for residential districts, specifically regarding setbacks and the possibility of small-scale commercial encroachment on corner lots?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
